title: I love how there are three different layers to Teemo...
body:
There's Teemo on the outside...
http://ddragon.leagueoflegends.com/cdn/img/champion/splash/Teemo_0.jpg
...a warm fuzzy Yordle who is loved by his comrades.

There's what Teemo is actually like on the inside...
http://ddragon.leagueoflegends.com/cdn/img/champion/splash/Teemo_8.jpg
...a deadly efficient and remorseless killer, and the most dangerous Yordle alive.

Then there's what we all know Teemo is on a spritual level...
http://ddragon.leagueoflegends.com/cdn/img/champion/splash/Teemo_14.jpg
...demon from the 9th circle of hell, infernal plight, and heart of darkness.

Teemo has layers. Onions have layers.
######~~Teemo onion skin when~~
